# Current Project State

Project initialized.

Memory Bank configured.

Backend development begins before frontend development.

React frontend will consume backend REST APIs.

Frontend home page is being built against the existing Spring Boot backend at `movie-ui-backend`.

---

# Current Goal

Build the dashboard home page in `movie-ui-frontend` using `GET /api/dashboard`.

Do not modify the backend from the frontend agent unless fully necessary — backend changes are handled separately.

